@Host = http://localhost:5122
@CustomerNumber = 987654321

### 1. Test 404 - Resource Not Found (English)
# Expected: Title: "Not Found", Detail: "User with key 12345 was not found."
GET {{Host}}/api/diagnostics/not-found
Accept-Language: en-US
X-Customer-Number: {{CustomerNumber}}

---

### 2. Test 404 - Resource Not Found (Turkish)
# Expected: Title: "Bulunamadı", Detail: "12345 anahtarlı Kullanıcı bulunamadı."
GET {{Host}}/api/diagnostics/not-found
Accept-Language: tr-TR
X-Customer-Number: {{CustomerNumber}}

---

### 3. Test 400 - Validation Errors
# Expected: Errors dictionary with localized messages. 
# Check logs to ensure 'Password' value is masked as '***'
GET {{Host}}/api/diagnostics/validation
Accept-Language: en-US
X-Customer-Number: {{CustomerNumber}}

---

### 4. Test 422 - Business Rule (Insufficient Funds)
# Expected: Detail formatted with args: "Insufficient funds. Required: 150 USD"
GET {{Host}}/api/diagnostics/business-rule
Accept-Language: en-US
X-Customer-Number: {{CustomerNumber}}

---

### 5. Test 401 - Framework Native (Option 1)
# Expected: Handled by GlobalProblemDetailsFactory via UseStatusCodePages
GET {{Host}}/api/diagnostics/unauthorized
Accept-Language: tr-TR
X-Customer-Number: {{CustomerNumber}}

---

### 6. Test 500 - Unhandled System Exception
# Expected: Generic localized error message. 
# If in Development, 'debug' property should contain the stack trace.
GET {{Host}}/api/diagnostics/unhandled
Accept-Language: en-US
X-Customer-Number: {{CustomerNumber}}
